3. Principle of Actio and reactio, the mutal force is the same.

&quot;An object with no unbalanced forces acting on it will naturally come to rest&quot; 

Correct Law: An object with no unbalanced forces acting on it will keep the same velocity

&quot;An unbalanced force causes an object to move with a constant velocity&quot;

Correct Law: An unbalanced force causes an object to accelerate

&quot;Larger objects apply larger forces to small objects&quot;

Correct Law: Large objects apply the same force to small objects.
